7 following basis:
8 …
9 (2) All other funds appropriated to the Fund for local government grants for the
10 acquisition of megasites determined pursuant to subdivision (1) of this
11 subsection. purposes described in subsection (a) of this section. A grant for
12 the acquisition of a megasite is limited to eighty-five percent (85%) of the
13 lesser of the property's purchase price or tax value. The percentage actually
14 provided in the grant shall be determined by EDPNC based on total
15 development needs for the megasite, prior investment in the megasite by one
